<div class="inner" id="msg_284489"><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote">引用</div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote">Hag Covens<br><br>When three hags of any type gather, they can form a coven to gain increased magical ability. Any combination of hags can form a coven, but green hags are the most common members of such foul gatherings.<br><br>Whenever all three hags of a particular coven are within 10 feet of one another, all three of them can work together to use any of the following spell-like abilities: animate dead, baleful polymorph (DC 18), blight (DC 17), bestow curse (DC 17), clairaudience/clairvoyance, charm monster (DC 17), commune, control weather, dream, forcecage, mind blank, mirage arcana (DC 18), reincarnate, speak with dead, veil (DC 19), vision.<br><br>All three hags must take a full-round action to take part in this form of cooperative magic. All coven spell-like abilities function at CL 9th (or at the highest CL available to the most powerful hag in the coven). The save DCs are Charisma-based, and function as if with a Charisma score of 16 unless one of the hags has a higher Charisma score, in which case the spell-like ability DCs are adjusted by that hag&#039;s Charisma modifier.<br><br>At the GM&#039;s discretion, certain more powerful hag covens might have additional spell-like abilities.</blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div><br><a href="http://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/monstrous-humanoids/hag/green-hag" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">PF</a>中关于鬼婆战队的叙述<br><br>无责任试译<br><br>当某个战团三个鬼婆彼此都在10呎内，她们三个可以一起工作，使用以下任何类法术能力： 操纵死尸， 恶意变形 （DC18）， 枯萎术 （DC17）， 降咒 （直流17）， 锐耳/鹰眼术， 魅惑怪物 （DC17）， 通神术， 操控天气， 讬梦法， 魔力监牢， 心灵屏障， 海市蜃楼 （DC18）， 转生术，死者交谈， 迷罩 （DC19）， 灵视。<br><br>三个鬼婆们必须一起进行一个整轮行动，来参与这种形式的仪式魔法。 所有类法术能力的施法者等级在9级（或者更高的施法者等级，依照战团中其中最强大的鬼婆）。豁免DC基于魅力和等级，如同16的魅力，除非之一的鬼婆具有更高的魅力值，在这种情况下，战团的类法术能力是依那个老太婆的魅力调整值调整。<br><br>ＧＭ决定，一些更强大的女巫战团可能有其他的类法术能力。<br><br>－　－<br>Coven本身是西方的巫者们对于所属巫师集会（通常指女巫）的一种特殊称呼，在传说中通常由12名女巫成员跟一个主席(有人说是恶魔)所组成。带有欧洲古代异教的宗教特征。在翻译上有时直接被译为柯文。<br><br>虽然个人看到绿鬼婆跟海鬼婆就很想把他叫做鬼婆战队。<br><br>老鬼婆：我是一号红鬼婆。<br>海鬼婆：我是二号蓝鬼婆。<br>绿鬼婆：我是三号绿鬼婆。<br><br>我们是鬼婆战队～～<br><br>PC冒险者骑士：好恐怖的感觉...这一定是个幻觉吓不倒我的.....囧&quot;</div>
